import {
  EachPostLi,
  Footer,
  FooterBig,
  FooterSmall,
  Header,
  LoadingDiv,
  LoadingImg,
  Main,
  MediaDiv,
  PagenumberDiv,
  PagingSection,
  PostLink,
  PostListDiv,
  PostRepl,
  PostSection,
  PostTitle,
  PostTitleDiv,
  SlogunBig,
  SlogunSection,
  SlogunSmall,
  SubHeaderDiv,
  TitleBig,
  TitleLogoDiv,
  TitleSmall,
} from "./styledComponent.js";

import {
  faSun,
  faMoon,
  faArrowsRotate,
  faPenToSquare,
  faLocationPin,
  faArrowLeft,
  faArrowRight,
} from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from "@fortawesome/react-fontawesome";
import { faReact } from "@fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons";

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <MediaDiv>
        <Header>
          <TitleLogoDiv>
            <TitleBig>으앙</TitleBig>
            <TitleSmall>졸리다</TitleSmall>
          </TitleLogoDiv>
          <SubHeaderDiv>다크모드 버튼</SubHeaderDiv>
        </Header>
        <Main>
          <SlogunSection>
            <SlogunBig>우리가 하는 것 </SlogunBig>
            <SlogunSmall>이거이거 이거이거 진행한다.</SlogunSmall>
          </SlogunSection>

          <PostSection>
            <PostTitleDiv>
              <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faArrowsRotate} />
              <PostTitle>내 코디</PostTitle>
            </PostTitleDiv>
          </PostSection>
        </Main>
        <Footer></Footer>
      </MediaDiv>
    </>
  );
}

export default App;
